  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Galaxy Kart is an arcade kart racing game focused on combat and the individual skill of each driver.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a galaxy full of crazy racers, a frantic championship decides who is the best driver of all! 🏁</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENHANCE THE BATTLE WITH ITEMS AND SKILLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the unique skills of each character and grab power-ups to make your way to the finish line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/8598f45cfc365e00423128e3b9ba5e22.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/8598f45cfc365e00423128e3b9ba5e22.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/8598f45cfc365e00423128e3b9ba5e22.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RACE IN DIFFERENT GALAXIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a wide variety of maps, whether in a quick match or a tournament.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/1663f7d95daa40554899f47cf731c329.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/1663f7d95daa40554899f47cf731c329.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/1663f7d95daa40554899f47cf731c329.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PERSONALIZE YOUR RACER & KART</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new characters and karts and mix and match from a wide range of unique combinations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/982ccc54d17ba551085f9b47c4061744.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/982ccc54d17ba551085f9b47c4061744.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/982ccc54d17ba551085f9b47c4061744.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHALLENGE YOUR OPPONENTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against bots or compete with other players in online matches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Galaxy Kart brings the ultimate racing experience, filled with boosted features, including:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 Unique Courses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Tournaments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Characters with unique skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Power-Ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Levels of Difficulties (Easy, Normal, Hard and Challenge)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Players Multiplayer Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice-Chat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/b55532e40ed05e28d8b82533fc0a009d.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/b55532e40ed05e28d8b82533fc0a009d.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/b55532e40ed05e28d8b82533fc0a009d.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in this energetic kart game and drive among the stars using the movements of your HANDS!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear up, strap in, and prepare to embark on an unforgettable journey through the COSMOS! 🌌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JOIN OUR DISCORD = </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/3b910f22f05ecc21fed69f9a802982a7.avif?t=1734124508\" width=777 height=249 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Galaxy Kart is an arcade kart racing game focused on combat and the individual skill of each driver.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a galaxy full of crazy racers, a frantic championship decides who is the best driver of all! 🏁</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>ENHANCE THE BATTLE WITH ITEMS AND SKILLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the unique skills of each character and grab power-ups to make your way to the finish line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/8598f45cfc365e00423128e3b9ba5e22.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/8598f45cfc365e00423128e3b9ba5e22.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/8598f45cfc365e00423128e3b9ba5e22.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>RACE IN DIFFERENT GALAXIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a wide variety of maps, whether in a quick match or a tournament.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/1663f7d95daa40554899f47cf731c329.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/1663f7d95daa40554899f47cf731c329.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/1663f7d95daa40554899f47cf731c329.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PERSONALIZE YOUR RACER & KART</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new characters and karts and mix and match from a wide range of unique combinations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/982ccc54d17ba551085f9b47c4061744.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/982ccc54d17ba551085f9b47c4061744.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/982ccc54d17ba551085f9b47c4061744.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHALLENGE YOUR OPPONENTS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against bots or compete with other players in online matches.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Galaxy Kart brings the ultimate racing experience, filled with boosted features, including:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >18 Unique Courses</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Tournaments</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10 Characters with unique skills</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9 Power-Ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 Levels of Difficulties (Easy, Normal, Hard and Challenge)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Players Multiplayer Mode</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Voice-Chat</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/b55532e40ed05e28d8b82533fc0a009d.poster.avif?t=1734124508\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/b55532e40ed05e28d8b82533fc0a009d.webm?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/b55532e40ed05e28d8b82533fc0a009d.mp4?t=1734124508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in this energetic kart game and drive among the stars using the movements of your HANDS!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gear up, strap in, and prepare to embark on an unforgettable journey through the COSMOS! 🌌</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >JOIN OUR DISCORD = </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1401970/extras/3b910f22f05ecc21fed69f9a802982a7.avif?t=1734124508\" width=777 height=249 /></span></p>",
